---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import CTAButton from '../components/CTAButton.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Tjenester - Nettup"
  description="Komplett oversikt over våre webutviklingstjenester. Fra webdesign og netthandel til CMS-løsninger og vedlikehold."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-indigo-100 py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
          Våre <span class="text-blue-600">tjenester</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-600 mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          [Spesifikasjon kommer] - Alt du trenger for å lykkes digitalt
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Intro tekst -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center">
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          [Spesifikasjon kommer] - Hos Nettup tilbyr vi en komplett pakke med
          webutviklingstjenester. Fra første idé til ferdig lansert nettside, og
          alt vedlikehold etterpå - vi har deg dekket. Vårt mål er å skape
          digitale løsninger som ikke bare ser bra ut, men som også leverer
          målbare resultater for din bedrift.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Webdesign & UX/UI -->
  <section id="webdesign" class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
            <div
              class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-4"
            >
              <svg
                class="w-8 h-8 text-white"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M7 21a4 4 0 01-4-4V5a2 2 0 012-2h4a2 2 0 012 2v12a4 4 0 01-4 4zM21 5a2 2 0 00-2-2h-4a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a4 4 0 004 4h4a2 2 0 002-2V5z"
                ></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900">
              Webdesign & UX/UI
            </h2>
          </div>

          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
            [Spesifikasjon kommer] - Vi lager moderne, responsivt design som
            ikke bare ser fantastisk ut, men som også er optimalisert for
            konvertering og brukeropplevelse.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">
            Typiske leveranser:
          </h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg
                class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3 mt-1"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700"
                >[Spesifikasjon kommer] - Brukersentrert design</span
              >
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg
                class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3 mt-1"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700"
                >[Spesifikasjon kommer] - Responsivt design for alle enheter</span
              >
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg
                class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3 mt-1"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700"
                >[Spesifikasjon kommer] - Konverteringsoptimalisering</span
              >
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg
                class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3 mt-1"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700"
                >[Spesifikasjon kommer] - Tilgjengelighetsoptimalisering</span
              >
            </li>
          </ul>

          <CTAButton
            text="Book en uforpliktende konsultasjon"
            onclick="openCalendly()"
            size="lg"
          />
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
          <div
            class="h-64 bg-gray-200 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center"
          >
            <span class="text-gray-500">[Design mockup kommer]</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Netthandel & betalingsløsninger -->
  <section id="netthandel" class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div class="lg:order-2">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
            <div
              class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-4"
            >
              <svg
                class="w-8 h-8 text-white"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M3 3h2l.4 2M7 13h10l4-8H5.4m0 0L7 13m0 0l-2.293 2.293c-.63.63-.184 1.707.707 1.707H17M17 13v4a2 2 0 01-2 2H9a2 2 0 01-2-2v-4m8 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2H9a2 2 0 00-2 2v4.01"
                ></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900">
              Netthandel & betalingsløsninger
            </h2>
          </div>

          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
            [Spesifikasjon kommer] - Vi bygger kraftige e-handelsløsninger som
            øker salget ditt. Fra produktkatalog til betalingsintegrasjon - alt
            er optimalisert for konvertering.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Inkludert:</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg
                class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3 mt-1"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700"
                >[Spesifikasjon kommer] - Produktkatalog med søk og filtrering</span
              >
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg
                class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3 mt-1"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700"
                >[Spesifikasjon kommer] - Stripe & Klarna integrasjon</span
              >
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg
                class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3 mt-1"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700"
                >[Spesifikasjon kommer] - Handlekurv og checkout-optimalisering</span
              >
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg
                class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3 mt-1"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700"
                >[Spesifikasjon kommer] - Ordrehåndtering og lagerintegrasjon</span
              >
            </li>
          </ul>

          <CTAButton
            text="Book en uforpliktende konsultasjon"
            onclick="openCalendly()"
            size="lg"
          />
        </div>

        <div class="lg:order-1 bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-lg">
          <div
            class="h-64 bg-white rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center shadow-md"
          >
            <span class="text-gray-500">[E-handel mockup kommer]</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CMS-integrasjon & Headless -->
  <section id="cms" class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
            <div
              class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-4"
            >
              <svg
                class="w-8 h-8 text-white"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M4 7v10c0 2.21 3.582 4 8 4s8-1.79 8-4V7M4 7c0 2.21 3.582 4 8 4s8-1.79 8-4M4 7c0-2.21 3.582-4 8-4s8 1.79 8 4m0 5c0 2.21-3.582 4-8 4s-8-1.79-8-4"
                ></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900">
              CMS-integrasjon & Headless
            </h2>
          </div>

          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
            [Spesifikasjon kommer] - Vi implementerer fleksible innholdssystemer
            som gjør det enkelt for deg å oppdatere innholdet selv, uansett
            teknisk bakgrunn.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">
            Løsninger vi tilbyr:
          </h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg
                class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3 mt-1"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700"
                >[Spesifikasjon kommer] - WordPress tilpassede løsninger</span
              >
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg
                class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3 mt-1"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700"
                >[Spesifikasjon kommer] - Headless CMS arkitektur</span
              >
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg
                class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3 mt-1"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700"
                >[Spesifikasjon kommer] - API-baserte løsninger</span
              >
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg
                class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3 mt-1"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700"
                >[Spesifikasjon kommer] - Opplæring og dokumentasjon</span
              >
            </li>
          </ul>

          <CTAButton
            text="Book en uforpliktende konsultasjon"
            onclick="openCalendly()"
            size="lg"
          />
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
          <div
            class="h-64 bg-gray-200 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center"
          >
            <span class="text-gray-500">[CMS interface mockup kommer]</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Vedlikehold & Support -->
  <section id="support" class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div class="lg:order-2">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
            <div
              class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-4"
            >
              <svg
                class="w-8 h-8 text-white"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M18.364 5.636l-3.536 3.536m0 5.656l3.536 3.536M9.172 9.172L5.636 5.636m3.536 9.192L5.636 18.364M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0zm-5 0a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z"
                ></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900">
              Vedlikehold & Support
            </h2>
          </div>

          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
            [Spesifikasjon kommer] - Din nettside trenger regelmessig
            vedlikehold for å holde seg sikker, rask og oppdatert. Vi tilbyr
            forskjellige SLA-nivåer tilpasset dine behov.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">
            Support-tjenester:
          </h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg
                class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3 mt-1"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700"
